---
title: Pork & Apple Burger with Rosemary Wedges and Rocket Salad
description: Pork and apple is a classic combination and everyone loves a burger. Take those two ideas, add a bit of HelloFresh magic and what have you got? A pork and apple burger, that's what! Add some rosemary wedges and a fresh rocket salad and it's a guaranteed crowd-pleaser. Our tip is to take the pork out of your fridge around 45 mins before using - bringing it up to room temperature means the burgers cook more evenly. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-apple-burger-86555451-a45d1e9a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/pork-apple-burger-5f7f1e7a4a1941133f0f31cb-454ea996.pdf
